Simple client and server vtTLS command-line applications

Installation:
make clean
make

Server arguments:
server <port> 

Client arguments:
client <ip> <port> <useKnock> <file-to-download> <file-to-save>

Example:
./server 2000
./client 127.0.0.1 2000 knock files/Tux.png MyTux.png
./client 127.0.0.1 2000 dontKnock files/Tux.png MyTux.png

Available files:
- test100k.txt --- 100KB text file with random chars
- test1m.txt   --- 1MB text file with random chars
- test10m.txt  --- 10MB text file with random chars

